divs: Sighting DetailsIt (lights)shot up from the ground and was dancing around, was near the Ho-chunk barrial grounds, has always felt there was something about that ground. Heard a story of a crash of a UFO in the early 1900. Object went up and down, side to side, would like an investigator to come out to the sight before the winter sets in in December. June the 28th took his camera out and saw military jets flying around the area. does not know of a military instation in the area, has video on TV.
